{"tid":977540,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年1月3日 【大師午間教路】恒指升到25500點做淡！","createTime":"2019-01-11T09:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T01:48:46.000Z","uid":66271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e96003efde5395dba1b1745505253380036a65a8","tid":977540,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190104/photo/bkn-20190104122809219-0104_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190104125357\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190104122809219-0104_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190104125357&h=50554858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈表示，港股周五(4日)低開後中段挾上，無跟美股下跌，但他強調，此走勢「見慣見熟」，因港股今年開局首日已跌700點，「跌定落黎」，故反彈屬正常。<br />\n<br />\n大師認為，挾倉之下大市或反彈至25,500點，但反覆尋底格局未變，故宜逢高做淡，續持淡倉。至於中美貿易代表下周談判，他認為結果難料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a432b430956beefe38712f79f6501d78bd8207","tid":977540,"uid":186594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8343df031cc127d948526f02efc0440766ab9432","tid":977540,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"屌你bin cfu c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ca062127392206e3fd61e7de7d44df2ca60f38","tid":977540,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"cfu無錯，係市場扭曲"},{"pid":"975ccdf989808ca7bcedb298498c820c3c2c0c23","tid":977540,"uid":